title: Antique Trader Antiques Collectibles Price Guide 2015 - Gooner
description:
Publisher: Krause Publications; Thirty-first Edition edition (October 1, 2014)
Language: English
ISBN-10: 1440240914
ISBN-13: 978-1440240911

Filled with more than 4,300 new color images, expert insight on everything from cherished classics to the latest trends, and vetted values throughout help to once again make the Antique Trader Antiques & Collectibles the premiere reference in the field. For three decades, Antique Trader has been your trusted guide to the finest collections, the best advice, and the most reliable resources available in the market. The goal of this comprehensive guide has always been to inform and educate so you can buy and sell with confidence. Achieving that goal is why Antique Trader Antiques & Collectibles is the best-selling annual guide on the market. You will enjoy advertising, art, ceramics, Coca-Cola collectibles, coin-ops, comic books, dolls, firearms, furniture, glass, jewelry, kitchenware, lamps & lighting, music memorabilia, postcards, quilts and hooked rugs, salesman samples, silver, toys, World War II collectibles, and more!
